{"tid":1744551,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我系韓國讀書 而我都識一堆中國朋友...","createTime":"2019-11-21T19:55:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T20:34:57.000Z","uid":340626,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"91f425a321a771771c7b4639af33d2728b7f4356","tid":1744551,"uid":340626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T19:55:06.000Z","msg":"是咁的 我讀個間就好鬼死多中國人<br />\n仲要我個科識到嘅都系韓國同中國人<br />\n一開始大家都好地地 吾會啲咩因為我系香港人 佢地系中國人而點點點<br />\n但系最近睇朋友圈（因為有一科老師識中文 啲功課佢都會擺朋友圈 又會系群組到講上堂內容 所以迫住要用wechat）<br />\n佢地開始分享新聞 連學校支持香港既大字報都會擺出黎<br />\n再講埋啲難聽既說話 我都吾知好冇反擊/留言好...<br />\n當然佢地只系小部份 我識好多都系支持香港 明白事理既中國人<br />\n第一次開po sorry for 1999😭<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jzypNyw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjzypNyw.jpg&h=b6d8c84a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dd4ac45b454d009a6cc2950a3856867a639742c9","tid":1744551,"uid":179729,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T20:00:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8p6KNBB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8p6KNBB.jpg&h=62174693&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee52f0de99007cf835f02699ac25007de7f11040","tid":1744551,"uid":184233,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T20:03:43.000Z","msg":"系你老母咩"},{"pid":"5ecd88580ac60d050b3fefcf34db181e50fa87cd","tid":1744551,"uid":306337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T20:04:15.000Z","msg":"系你老母 你老母系"},{"pid":"bd7912cd72a703317bd9c4fb0a08e37c6c7e3628","tid":1744551,"uid":116105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd4ac45b454d009a6cc2950a3856867a639742c9","tid":1744551,"uid":179729,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T20:00:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8p6KNBB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8p6KNBB.jpg&h=62174693&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T20:04:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/ass